snippet.textDisplay:
UHU is a German glue.
UHU GmbH & Co. KG is a Germany manufacturerof adhesive products products, based in Bühl, Germany.
Fischer named the glue UHU (pronounced "ooo-hoo", though in many English-speaking countries it is said "you-hoo") after Uhu, the onomatopoeiac German name of the eagle-owl , a bird which at the time could still be found in the Black Forest.
snippet.textOriginal:
